## Tansu

Platform wheels ship a precompiled `tansu` executable (`calfkit_mesh/bin/`),
built from unmodified Tansu source. Only compile-time feature selection is
applied: `cargo build --release -p tansu --bin tansu --no-default-features
--features dynostore`.

- Source:    https://github.com/tansu-io/tansu
- Version:   v0.6.0 (commit 079c4c334a0e9240933d208ecd38c1127526e89c), obtained 2026-07-01
- License:   Apache-2.0 (same license text as in LICENSE)
- Copyright: Peter Morgan <peter.morgan@tansu.io> and contributors

Upstream Tansu distributes no NOTICE file of its own (verified at tag v0.6.0).
